=====================================================================
TCP vs UDP
=====================================================================

TCP:
- TCP use hota hai jab reliability chahiye
- Ordered delivery
- Packet loss recover karta hai
- Connection-oriented (handshake hota hai)

Used in:
- HTTPS
- Login systems
- Banking
- File downloads
- APIs


UDP:
- UDP use hota hai jab speed important ho
- No reliability guarantee
- No ordering guarantee
- Connectionless (no handshake)

Used in:
- DNS
- Online gaming
- Video calls
- Live streaming
- VoIP

